    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fabric with a short woolen pile, usually of mohair, and resembling velvet. Used to produce tapestries, upholstery of soft furnishings, and formal dress.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
